	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-175221699" class="story-title"> <a   href="//news.slashdot.org/story/24/10/09/1939254/how-the-us-lost-the-solar-power-race-to-china">How the US Lost the Solar Power Race To China</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-opinion-how-us-lost-solar-power-race-to-china/"  title="External link - https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-opinion-how-us-lost-solar-power-race-to-china/" target="_blank"> (bloomberg.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
